  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden Cats: Magic Forest is a hidden object game where you'll search for hidden cats while exploring the mysteries of the magical forest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688720/extras/8aa9f6524d5123d1f6b32d6ef7ae5075.poster.avif?t=1729066656\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688720/extras/8aa9f6524d5123d1f6b32d6ef7ae5075.webm?t=1729066656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688720/extras/8aa9f6524d5123d1f6b32d6ef7ae5075.mp4?t=1729066656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find cats in black, white, and orange colors. Lift old trees and plant saplings in their place to create new trees.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the Hidden Egyptian Cat God.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn interesting facts about cats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Touch the magical texture of the forest and interact with other surprise objects to earn all the achievements.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you enjoy games like \"A Building Full of Cats\" and \"Hidden Through Time,\" <strong>Hidden Cats: Magic Forest</strong> could be a perfect choice for you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688720/extras/9c85704c0ffe70aa53e0923ccf7145da.poster.avif?t=1729066656\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688720/extras/9c85704c0ffe70aa53e0923ccf7145da.webm?t=1729066656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688720/extras/9c85704c0ffe70aa53e0923ccf7145da.mp4?t=1729066656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden Cats: Magic Forest is a hidden object game where you'll search for hidden cats while exploring the mysteries of the magical forest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688720/extras/8aa9f6524d5123d1f6b32d6ef7ae5075.poster.avif?t=1729066656\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688720/extras/8aa9f6524d5123d1f6b32d6ef7ae5075.webm?t=1729066656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688720/extras/8aa9f6524d5123d1f6b32d6ef7ae5075.mp4?t=1729066656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find cats in black, white, and orange colors. Lift old trees and plant saplings in their place to create new trees.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the Hidden Egyptian Cat God.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn interesting facts about cats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Touch the magical texture of the forest and interact with other surprise objects to earn all the achievements.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you enjoy games like \"A Building Full of Cats\" and \"Hidden Through Time,\" <strong>Hidden Cats: Magic Forest</strong> could be a perfect choice for you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688720/extras/9c85704c0ffe70aa53e0923ccf7145da.poster.avif?t=1729066656\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688720/extras/9c85704c0ffe70aa53e0923ccf7145da.webm?t=1729066656\" type=\"video/webm; codec